messages.ssml: <speak>Do you mean COVID-19? The World Health Organization announced a name for the disease that is causing the 2019 novel coronavirus outbreak, which was first identified in Wuhan, China. The name of this disease is coronavirus disease 2019, abbreviated as COVID-19. In COVID-19, ‘CO’ stands for ‘corona,’ ‘VI’ for ‘virus,’ and ‘D’ for disease.</speak>
